### Description

Right now there is no possibility to update the form field value based on the value changes of another one without using effect.

### Proposed solution

The ideal solution would to be to be able to declare it in the schema like this.
value = signal({ value1: { nestedProp: undefined }, value2: undefined });
form(this.value, path => {
    reset(path.value2, { computation: ({ valueOf }) => valueOf(path.value1).nestedProp });
});

it would use linkedSignal internally.

### Alternatives considered

none

